<main class="story-content">
<p>Vera gathered her team in a hidden classroom basement, whispering urgently.</p>
<p>"Luna, Cyra, Rogue, Shade, we need to make Isabella’s company crumble from within," Vera said.</p>
<p>They had one advantage: by day, they blended perfectly as students, attending lectures, taking notes, and appearing harmless.</p>
<p>Their disguises allowed them to move unnoticed within the university while secretly planning.</p>
<p>Meanwhile, Ethan and Isabella unknowingly crossed paths again during a lecture.</p>
<p>Their accidental encounters sparked curiosity and subtle hints of partnership.</p>
<p>Selena sent messages to the hacker team, providing inside intel about Isabella’s company systems.</p>
<p>Cyra smiled at the incoming information, fingers ready to exploit vulnerabilities.</p>
<p>Luna, the sniper, observed the scene outside the window, keeping the team safe.</p>
<p>Rogue and Shade prepared for physical interventions if needed.</p>
